{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/IMG4.jpg?t=1678806966\" /><br><br><strong>Magic Twins</strong> is a 1-2 <strong>co-operative arcade puzzle</strong> game in which Abra and Cadabra (the titular Magic Twins), must constantly swap their chromagic powers to defeat hordes of color elementals and stop the Colormageddon (which they unintentionally unleashed). Red beats red, blue beats blue.. you get the drill. Magic doesn't need to be complicated!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/Colormageddon.gif?t=1678806966\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/Communicate.png?t=1678806966\" /><br>Spells are not enough! <strong>Communication</strong> (and probably some yelling) will be invaluable to overcome all the challenges ahead of you: different objectives per level, bosses, multiple game modes, special events\u2026<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/Gameplay.gif?t=1678806966\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/Art.png?t=1678806966\" /><br>The game features 2D art with spooky kawaii vibes. Do you want cute skins? We have them!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/Great.gif?t=1678806966\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/Features.png?t=1678806966\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>COLORMAGEDDON.</strong> The end of the world comes in technicolour!<br></li><li><strong>COOPERATIVE.</strong> Coordinate with your friends and test your reflexes and the power of friendship to combine your chromagic powers.<br></li><li><strong>TONS OF CONTENT.</strong> Discover new areas of Mallorca island as you eliminate the threat in the initial areas and unlock new game modes, different enemies, secrets and secondary objectives.<br></li><li><strong>SIMPLE CONTROLS, UNIQUE CHALLENGES.</strong> Controlling the Magic Twins is simple, but each level has different objectives and turns in the mechanics.<br></li><li><strong>KAWAII.</strong> Unlock new theme skins for the sisters!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Toss a star to your witches","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270080/c711091532c3cbf35082de03559dff450b521b22.jpg"},{"name":"Who's the boss?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270080/dff2a5eccb9d2e56efb9f695e1ca2ce7b31c354d.jpg"},{"name":"All Star","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270080/8695b1d4a0957d47457ae2f3806b1f601b235297.jpg"},{"name":"DO IT FOR HER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270080/be5ca4a64e549e3709dffdc9b1dc793b605af3ac.jpg"},{"name":"Specialists","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270080/d9cc8a90961ff01165e3c94922bc6896dc8b9259.jpg"},{"name":"Ready for almost any occasion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270080/99936ccedd35a25db4b275715d549f168a5d97dc.jpg"},{"name":"It\u2019s a kind of magic ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270080/faa4b8fe7298bd42a3136258e512a004a2356ec3.jpg"},{"name":"Twin Symbiosis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270080/902dc6a5b59d8e433d6f73b5684d46cd15c002af.jpg"},{"name":"Chromagic indecision","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270080/d8fbb1ad9c3ddf51158987f223f1acaba092e930.jpg"},{"name":"Bomberwitch","path":"h